Revision history for Rose-DBx-Object-MoreHelpers

0.100 22 April 2014
 - fix primary_key_uri_escaped() to check explicitly for ref() eq ARRAY
   in case the primary key is an object (e.g. BigInt)

0.09 13 Nov 2012
 - added fetch_count() method (fcahoon@msi.umn.edu)
 - support column alias names in primary_key_value()

0.08 13 May 2010
 - change primary_key_uri_escaped() (again) to match
   CatalystX::CRUD::Controller, also escaping any / marks.

0.07 13 May 2010
 - change primary_key_uri_escaped() implementation to avoid sprintf().

0.06 10 Nov 2008
 - add moniker() and unique_value() methods

0.05 4 Nove 2008
 - oops. fix 0.04 fix to always turn **integer** not object.

0.04 4 Nov 2008
 - has_related() now checks if $self can $rel . _count and tries to handle
   it sanely if _count is not a method

0.03 16 Sept 2008
 - flatten now just a thin wrapper around as_tree() core Helper method

0.02 26 Aug 2008
 - add column_is_boolean method

0.01 20 Aug 2008
 - First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

